"hljs-meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="hljs-meta-keyword">html</span> <span class="hljs-meta-keyword">PUBLIC</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN&quot;</span> </span><span class="hljs-meta"><span class="hljs-meta-string">&quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd&quot;</span>&gt;</span></code></pre></li><li><p><strong>XHTML 1.0 Frameset</strong></p><blockquote><p>该 DTD 等同于 XHTML 1.0 Transitional，但允许框架集内容。</p></blockquote><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="hljs-meta-keyword">html</span> <span class="hljs-meta-keyword">PUBLIC</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Frameset//EN&quot;</span> </span><span class="hljs-meta"><span class="hljs-meta-string">&quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-frameset.dtd&quot;</span>&gt;</span></code></pre></li><li><p><strong>XHTML 1.1</strong></p><blockquote><p>该 DTD 等同于 XHTML 1.0 Strict，但允许添加模型（例如提供对东亚语系的 ruby 支持）。</p></blockquote><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="hljs-meta-keyword">html</span> <span class="hljs-meta-keyword">PUBLIC</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.1//EN&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml11/DTD/xhtml11.dtd&quot;</span>&gt;</span></code></pre></li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="lt-a-gt-标签"><a href="#lt-a-gt-标签" class="headerlink" title="&lt;a&gt; 标签"></a><code>&lt;a&gt;</code> 标签</h4><ul><li><strong>实例</strong></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    
